Warm November promotes fairs in Kiev: where to buy products at affordable prices

06 Nov 2019, 07:25

Today, fairs will take place in six areas of the capital
On Wednesday, November 6, seasonal fairs will be held in Kiev, which provides for the sale of agricultural products and their products for all product groups. This was reported in the Department of Industry and Entrepreneurship Development of Kyiv City State Administration.
So today the fairs will take place:

in Holosiivskyi district - Strategic Highway (within the limits of Nauky Ave. and Malokitaivska Street), str. Demiyivska, 45-47;
in Darnytskyi district - просп. Mykola Bazhana (footpath from Arcadia shopping mall to Osokorky metro station), intersection of Pavel Chubynsky and Yuriy Paskhalin streets, ul. Anna Akhmatova, 31;
in Desnyanskiy district - st. Electrotechnical (from WOG - 2, 4-B, 6, 16, 10, 18, 26, 28, and from the other side - 5, 5-A, 7, 11, 9, 9-A to SHELL; Electrotechnical , 2-A, opposite the central entrance of the markets "Obriy-2000" and "Gloria-T");
in Dniprovs'kyi district - ave. Sobornosti, 2-20;
in the Pechersk district - st. Velyka Vasylkivska (within the streets of Jerzy Giedroyc and Kovpak);
in Podilskyi district - ave. True, 5-11.

As reported, the fairs in the capital will last until the end of the week.
By the way, President of Ukraine Volodymyr Zelensky was offered to create a special body to control the prices of products. A corresponding petition is registered on the President's website.
